          {
            "title": "End of the Game",
            "contents":"[To be read out by the Host.]\nThank you all, folks, for helping straighten out our little town's problems here tonight. It's been a rocky road, but we made it through! If you'd like to relax and gather round now, let's all find out what was really going on?",
